    {
      "id": "69f1ad05a3aa7ec103b3d5e9",
      "text": "Wikipedia のダンプ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446151
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d53",
      "text": "from [2026/04/27inajobの父のパソコン選び]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446151
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d54",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446171
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d56",
      "text": "Wikipedia のダンプがある[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d57",
      "text": "\thttps://dumps.wikimedia.org/",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d58",
      "text": "\tzim という独自の形式で圧縮されている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d59",
      "text": " \t[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/ZIM_(ファイルフォーマット) ZIM_(ファイルフォーマット)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d5a",
      "text": "\thttps://dumps.wikimedia.org/other/kiwix/zim/wikipedia/",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d5b",
      "text": "\t\t全 Wikipedia のデータ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d5c",
      "text": "\t\t\t全言語の Wikipedia のダンプデータ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d5d",
      "text": "\t圧縮データで 878.134 GB、画像を削除した圧縮データで 287.515 GB ある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d5e",
      "text": "\t\t画像を削除した圧縮データが有るということは圧縮データの方は画像を含めてのデータということ……。凄まじい。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d5f",
      "text": "\t\t単位合ってるかなー……。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d60",
      "text": "\t\t2年前に110GBでダウンロードできる話をしている人がいたから多分合ってる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d61",
      "text": "\t\t[https://www.reddit.com/r/DataHoarder/comments/1fccptq/did_you_know_you_can_download_all_of_wikipedia_in/ Did You Know You Can Download All of Wikipedia in under 110 GB?]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446177
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1ad0600000000009a8d62",
      "text": "\t今年中に TB 行きそう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777446151,
      "updated": 1777446235
    },
